Program can be compiled using makefile.
$ make

Following parameters could be used (in any order):
	-N for no. of nodes (default : 2)
	-M for max packets (default : 10)
	-PR for packet genration rate (default : 1000)(lines for this are commented in the submitted code)
	-W for window size (default : 2)
	-L for packet length (default : 10)
	-P for packet generation probability (default : 0.5)
	-d for debug mode (default : false)

Shell script could be executed using following command:
$ ./SlottedAloha.sh

UNIX Script file has recorded, and could replayed using:
$ scriptreplay --timing=SlottedAloha.txt SlottedAloha.log